ext": "2,245", "bbox": [753.5, 641.9, 796.9, 659.6]}, {"text": "1,885", "bbox": [944.2, 641.9, 984.4, 659.6]}, {"text": "Net property, plant and equipment", "bbox": [56.3, 668.0, 305.0, 685.7]}, {"text": "$4,038", "bbox": [743.8, 668.0, 796.9, 685.7]}, {"text": "$4,085", "bbox": [935.2, 668.0, 984.4, 685.7]}, {"text": "The Company capitalized interest costs of $9 million in 2002, $3 million in 2001 and $2 million in 2000 as part of the cost of", "bbox": [81.3, 728.4, 953.5, 746.1]}, {"text": "major asset construction projects. Approximately $137 million will be required to complete construction projects in progress at", "bbox": [56.2, 754.4, 962.1, 772.1]}, {"text": "September 28, 2002.", "bbox": [56.2, 780.5, 206.1, 798.2]}, {"text": "Note 8: Other Current Liabilities", "bbox": [56.3, 822.9, 363.3, 843.7]}, {"text": "Other current liabilities at September 28, 2002 and September 29, 2001 include:", "bbox": [56.3, 851.3, 624.4, 869.0]}, {"text": "in millions", "bbox": [922.0, 878.9, 984.4, 894.5]}, {"text": "2002", "bbox": [762.8, 904.9, 796.9, 920.6]}, {"text": "2001", "bbox": [953.8, 904.9, 984.4, 920.6]}, {"text": "Accrued salaries, wages and benefits", "bbox": [56.3, 933.6, 314.7, 951.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [743.8, 933.6, 753.5, 951.3]}, {"text": "308", "bbox": [767.9, 933.6, 796.9, 951.3]}, {"text": "$270", "bbox": [948.6, 933.6, 984.4, 951.3]}, {"text": "Self insurance reserves", "bbox": [56.3, 959.6, 217.9, 977.3]}, {"text": "225", "bbox": [767.9, 959.6, 796.9, 977.3]}, {"text": "189", "bbox": [957.6, 959.6, 984.4, 977.3]}, {"text": "Income taxes payable", "bbox": [56.2, 985.7, 208.9, 1003.4]}, {"text": "202", "bbox": [767.9, 985.7, 796.9, 1003.4]}, {"text": "109", "bbox": [957.6, 985.7, 984.4, 1003.4]}, {"text": "Property and other taxes", "bbox": [56.2, 1011.7, 234.4, 1029.4]}, {"text": "52", "bbox": [777.6, 1011.7, 796.9, 1029.4]}, {"text": "63", "bbox": [966.5, 1011.7, 984.4, 1029.4]}, {"text": "Other", "bbox": [56.3, 1037.7, 100.3, 1055.5]}, {"text": "297", "bbox": [767.9, 1037.7, 796.9, 1055.5]}, {"text": "226", "bbox": [957.6, 1037.7, 984.4, 1055.5]}, {"text": "Total other current liabilities", "bbox": [56.3, 1063.8, 255.9, 1081.5]}, {"text": "$1,084", "bbox": [743.8, 1063.8, 796.9, 1081.5]}, {"text": "$857", "bbox": [948.6, 1063.8, 984.4, 1081.5]}, {"text": "Note 9: Commitments", "bbox": [56.3, 1115.6, 266.2, 1136.4]}, {"text": "The Company leases certain farms and other properties and equipment for which the total rentals thereon approximated $105 million", "bbox": [56.3, 1144.0, 987.3, 1161.7]}, {"text": "in 2002, $76 million in 2001 and $66 million in 2000. Most farm leases have terms ranging from one to 10 years with various renewal", "bbox": [56.3, 1170.0, 971.1, 1187.7]}, {"text": "periods. The most significant obligations assumed under the terms of the leases are the upkeep of the facilities and payments of", "bbox": [56.3, 1196.1, 938.7, 1213.8]}, {"text": "insurance and property taxes.", "bbox": [56.3, 1222.1, 263.1, 1239.8]}, {"text": "Minimum lease commitments under non-cancelable leases at September 28, 2002, total $197 million composed of $72 million", "bbox": [81.3, 1248.2, 970.5, 1265.9]}, {"text": "for 2003, $41 million for 2004, $31 million for 2005, $25 million for 2006, $17 million for 2007 and $11 million for later years. These", "bbox": [56.3, 1274.2, 981.0, 1291.9]}, {"text": "future commitments are expected to be offset by future minimum lease payments to be received under subleases of approximately", "bbox": [56.3, 1300.2, 987.1, 1318.0]}, {"text": "$5 million.", "bbox": [56.3, 1326.3, 130.1, 1344.0]}, {"text": "The Company assists certain of its swine and chicken growers in obtaining financing for growout facilities by providing the", "bbox": [81.3, 1352.3, 942.9, 1370.0]}, {"text": "growers with extended growout contracts and conditional operation of the facilities should a grower default under their growout", "bbox": [56.3, 1378.4, 976.9, 1396.1]}, {"text": "or loan agreement. The Company also guarantees debt of outside third parties of $66 million.", "bbox": [56.3, 1404.4, 719.0, 1422.1]}, {"text": "The Company enters into various future purchase commitments for finished live cattle and hogs. These purchase commitments", "bbox": [81.3, 1430.5, 984.7, 1448.2]}, {"text": "are at a market-derived price at the time of delivery or were fully hedged if the price was determined at an earlier date. The", "bbox": [56.3, 1456.5, 936.4, 1474.2]}, {"text": "commitments deliverable in any year is less than the operating requirements of that year.", "bbox": [56.3, 1482.5, 685.2, 1500.2]}, {"text": "Tyson Foods, Inc. 2002 annual report", "bbox": [56.3, 155.5, 269.3, 169.0]}]}